CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 16, 1961, pg. A11, reads: "Meet the Springers - Brilliant Young Couple Manages to Combine Marriage and Career! - Co-Authors - Eric Springer (left) and Nathan Hershey look over one of the Hospital Law Manuals which they co-authored. Nathan also was in Springers' wedding party. - All Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Eric Springer holding Hospital Law Manual, and Nathan Hershey holding cigarette, seated behind desk, in office
